main event: Two photographs were taken of a mysterious object in the sky, appearing to leave a fluffy trail resembling smoke or cloud.
interesting points: The trail left by the object is discontinuous and fragmented, indicating motion,The brightness and density of the trail vary,There is a possibility of a small, solid-looking object at the front of the trail in both images,The photographs are believed to capture an unidentified flying object (UFO),The images were credited to photographer Al Asnis.
sighted object: a mysterious object leaving a fluffy trail in the sky
